g how the theory works in practice. This is an invaluable and fun tool for developing young children's understanding of their feelings and relationships."--cProvided by publisher.  a29 41 0aPreschool teaching. 0aEducation, PreschoolxActivity programs. 0aNursery world/Routledge essential guides for early years practitioners.  aLB 1140.3 M67 2015c1hUAED-Bi0162035203189  aLB 1140.3 M67 2015wLCc1i0162035203189d4/27/2015e3/24/2015lFLOOR_2mUAEDUCn3p$150.00rYsYtBOOKu12/18/2014  aLB1140.3 .M67 2015wLCc1i1007432477d1/20/2015lON_SHELFmGR_MACEWANp$38.73rYsYtBOOKu1/15/201501ahttp://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/no00021184bhttp://viaf.org/viaf/259194995